  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK820">
<l>eṉaittuṅ kuṟukuta lōmpaṉ maṉaikkeḻīi </l>
<l>maṉṟiṟ paḻippār toṭarpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Avoid even the least approach to a contraction of friendship with those who would love you in private but ridicule you in public.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
